## Frontend (Vite) environment variables
#
# Local dev:
# - You can leave this unset and rely on Vite proxy (/api -> http://localhost:5000)
# - Or set it explicitly to call the backend directly.
#
# AWS/production:
# - Set this to your public backend origin (typically the same domain).
#
# Examples:
# VITE_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:5000
# VITE_BACKEND_URL=https://sadsweb.xyz
VITE_BACKEND_URL=

